Sparkling Shelter
Discworld ritual help
Sparkling Shelter

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Sparkling Shelter
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is a defensive ritual that calls into being tokens of your deity's
favour, which happen to block certain forms of attack entirely.  Due to the
fickle nature of deific blessings, however, these tokens are fleeting, and
also tend to vanish after protecting you.
.EP
